\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Adapter --> |<1min| Redis[Cache Layer]
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0end
