\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Flink --> |enrichment| Neo4j
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Flink --> |lookups| Redis
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Flink --> |insights| KafkaInsights[Insights Topic]
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0KafkaInsights --> FHIR[FHIR Store]
