\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 ## Conclusion
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 This enhanced architecture provides:
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 1. **Clear separation** between real-time patient data (<1 second) and near-real-time knowledge updates (<5 minutes)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 2. **Comprehensive CDC implementation** using Debezium for reliable change capture
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 3. **Sophisticated transformation logic** that handles complex mappings from RDF/OWL to property graphs
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 4. **Multi-destination insight distribution** with appropriate delivery guarantees for each sink
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 5. **Production-grade monitoring** to ensure both streams meet their SLAs
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 The system achieves the critical balance of maintaining authoritative knowledge integrity while providing the sub-second query performance required for real-time clinical decision support.
\f1\fs24 \
\
